com.thinkaurelius.titan.diskstorage.common

Class DistributedStoreManager.MaskedTimestamp

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.thinkaurelius.titan.diskstorage.common.DistributedStoreManager.MaskedTimestamp
  • Enclosing class:
    DistributedStoreManager

    public class DistributedStoreManager.MaskedTimestamp
extends Object
    Helper class to create the deletion and addition timestamps for a particular transaction. It needs to be ensured that the deletion time is prior to the addition time since some storage backends use the time to resolve conflicts.
